# NewSubmissionResponse

**Object**

The notary service’s response to a software submission.

## Declaration

```swift
object NewSubmissionResponse
```

## Discussion

You receive a structure of this type in response to a call to the [doc://com.apple.notaryapi/documentation/NotaryAPI/Submit-Software] endpoint. Use the temporary security credentials this response contains to make a call to Amazon S3 to upload your software.

## Objects

- **NewSubmissionResponse.Data**: Information that the notary service provides for uploading your software for notarization and tracking the submission.
- **NewSubmissionResponse.Meta**: An empty object.

## Software submission

- **Submit Software**: Start the process of uploading a new version of your software to the notary service.
- **NewSubmissionRequest**: Data that you provide when starting a submission to the notary service.
